    • Event
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Concert, Festival, Sport, TicketAnalytics
    public abstract class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    Description: This is an abstract class that has Event data. Class from Raul. This class will let its children (Concert, Sport, Festival) store the appropriated data from the excel file of eventList
